descriptionNullable:
Data provided here was collected from Hass Avocado Board - Category Data. 

This is an updated version of dataset already introduced to Kaggle. 

Here is the [link](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/neuromusic/avocado-prices) to the very first dataset uploaded by [Justin Kiggins](https://www.kaggle.com/neuromusic). And [another one ](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/valentinjoseph/avocado-sales-20152021-us-centric) by [Valentin Joseph](https://www.kaggle.com/valentinjoseph), an update aggregating data till 2021. 

*Note regarding the regions mentioned in dataset *

"region" includes both regions and key locations which are cities or sub-regions. The values for locations do not add up to that of regions. The following are regions, as described [here](https://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/avocado/vignettes/a_intro.html) (another description of the dataset)

- California,
- West,
- Plains,
- South Central,
- Southeast,
- Midsouth,
- Great Lakes,
- Northeast.
title: Avocado Prices and Sales Volume 2015-2023
subtitle: Avocado data updated till December 3, 2023
